Poem - Question here refers to text at https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vinu1A23/poems/main/Poem%20-%20Question

Perfect answer they seek (from student)
Precise stroke they want (from painter)
percent right approach they ask (from scientist)
Purpose of learning they ask (from teacher)
Per se have they asked you health?
per se have they asked you happiness?
